TODO: record the asciinema cast.

Headless recording is not available in the build environment. To produce this
file locally, run:

  npm run build
  asciinema rec assets/demo.cast -c "node dist/cli.js scan test/fixtures"

Or render a GIF instead with VHS (see assets/demo.tape):

  vhs assets/demo.tape

The README references this slot; once recorded, upload to asciinema.org and
replace the PLACEHOLDER id in the README's asciicast badge.
